{"tid":927199,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【好心冇好報】遭假乞兒打劫 美捐錢女子被捅死","createTime":"2018-12-04T04:13:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T05:17:29.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dd0d1a5c298092f23f9bffcf77c59f19adc15727","tid":927199,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:13:20.000Z","msg":"（北美通訊）馬里蘭州發生懷疑假扮露宿者行兇案件。巴爾的摩一名52歲女士，周六凌晨給錢露宿者後被搶銀包，她身中多刀，送院後不治。<br />\n事發於巴爾的摩東部，警方表示，54歲死者Jacquelyn Smith與丈夫及女兒，開車經過公屋Latrobe Homes附近時，看到一名年輕女子，疑似抱着一個嬰兒，坐在街上。女士身前豎了紙皮，上面寫着「請幫我餵我的嬰兒」（Please help me feed my baby）。善良的Smith把車窗放下，從銀包拿錢給該露宿者。<br />\n就在此時，一名陌生男子上前，先向Smith致謝，但之後企圖搶走她的銀包，雙方糾纏。最後，該男子拿出短刀，多次插向Smith後，帶着露宿女子逃去。Smith送院後不治。<br />\n目前，涉案男女仍然在逃，被警方通緝。巴爾的摩巿長皮尤（Catherine Pugh）提醒巿民切勿再調低車窗，捐錢給露宿者，慨嘆如此釀成命案一宗也嫌太多。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181204/large/1543860037_628f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181204%2Flarge%2F1543860037_628f.jpg&h=039bc133&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ac9329fe62f878815d3235fdf8c9bae955133be","tid":927199,"uid":110988,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:15:15.000Z","msg":"未睇內文 估錯國家地區<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a17c5f0cde93245f9d701b3f1abdd00e19c9ce2","tid":927199,"uid":73613,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:16:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"61951ddbb6dce3ba4fa5287edfd79165d4b6f387","tid":927199,"uid":66324,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:20:54.000Z","msg":"係美國避乞衣係常識吧，最好完全唔理佢地<br />\n仲要係baltimore...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c41a5453363a7c2d0154be547ada2021d04f1b","tid":927199,"uid":70183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:21:03.000Z","msg":"rip"},{"pid":"05110e6d2fad215d8f160eaf36e9065246fa3d0b","tid":927199,"uid":119409,"like":3